## 2. Maps JavaScript API

### 2.1 Map (Clase Principal)

```javascript
const { Map } = await google.maps.importLibrary("maps");

const map = new Map(document.getElementById("map"), {
  center: { lat: -33.45, lng: -70.65 },  // Santiago, Chile
  zoom: 13,
  mapId: "MI_MAP_ID",           // Para cloud styling
  mapTypeId: "roadmap",         // roadmap, satellite, hybrid, terrain
  disableDefaultUI: false,
  zoomControl: true,
  mapTypeControl: true,
  scaleControl: true,
  streetViewControl: true,
  rotateControl: true,
  fullscreenControl: true,
  gestureHandling: "cooperative", // cooperative, greedy, none, auto
  restriction: {                  // Restringir área visible
    latLngBounds: { north: -33.3, south: -33.6, west: -70.8, east: -70.5 },
    strictBounds: false
  }
});
```

### MapOptions principales:
| Opción | Tipo | Descripción |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `center` | LatLng | Centro del mapa |
| `zoom` | number | Nivel de zoom (0=mundo, 21=edificio) |
| `mapId` | string | ID para cloud-based styling |
| `mapTypeId` | string | roadmap, satellite, hybrid, terrain |
| `heading` | number | Rotación del mapa (0-360) |
| `tilt` | number | Inclinación (0 o 45 en zoom alto) |
| `minZoom` / `maxZoom` | number | Límites de zoom |
| `clickableIcons` | boolean | POIs clickeables |
| `backgroundColor` | string | Color de fondo |

### Eventos del Map:
```javascript
map.addListener("click", (e) => {
  console.log("Click en:", e.latLng.lat(), e.latLng.lng());
});
map.addListener("zoom_changed", () => console.log("Zoom:", map.getZoom()));
map.addListener("bounds_changed", () => console.log("Bounds:", map.getBounds()));
map.addListener("center_changed", () => console.log("Center:", map.getCenter()));
map.addListener("idle", () => console.log("Mapa idle (carga completa)"));
map.addListener("tilesloaded", () => console.log("Tiles cargados"));
```

### 2.2 AdvancedMarkerElement (Marcadores Modernos)

```javascript
const { AdvancedMarkerElement, PinElement } =
  await google.maps.importLibrary("marker");

// Marcador básico
const marker = new AdvancedMarkerElement({
  map: map,
  position: { lat: -33.4078, lng: -70.5755 },
  title: "Av. Kennedy 7100"
});

// Marcador con pin personalizado
const pin = new PinElement({
  background: "#FF0000",
  borderColor: "#CC0000",
  glyphColor: "#FFFFFF",
  glyph: "A",          // Texto o elemento DOM
  scale: 1.2
});
const customMarker = new AdvancedMarkerElement({
  map: map,
  position: { lat: -33.41, lng: -70.53 },
  content: pin.element,
  title: "Mi marcador custom"
});

// Marcador con HTML custom
const content = document.createElement("div");
content.innerHTML = '<div style="background:blue;color:white;padding:8px;border-radius:50%;">★</div>';
const htmlMarker = new AdvancedMarkerElement({
  map: map,
  position: { lat: -33.42, lng: -70.55 },
  content: content
});

// Evento click
marker.addListener("click", () => {
  const infoWindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow({
    content: "<h3>Av. Kennedy 7100</h3><p>Vitacura, Santiago</p>"
  });
  infoWindow.open({ anchor: marker, map });
});
```

### 2.3 InfoWindow

```javascript
const infoWindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow({
  content: "<h3>Título</h3><p>Descripción</p>",
  ariaLabel: "Info",
  maxWidth: 300,
  minWidth: 200,
  disableAutoPan: false
});
infoWindow.open({ anchor: marker, map: map });
infoWindow.close();
```

### 2.4 Layers (Capas)

```javascript
// Tráfico
const trafficLayer = new google.maps.TrafficLayer();
trafficLayer.setMap(map);

// Transporte público
const transitLayer = new google.maps.TransitLayer();
transitLayer.setMap(map);

// Ciclovías
const bikeLayer = new google.maps.BicyclingLayer();
bikeLayer.setMap(map);

// KML
const kmlLayer = new google.maps.KmlLayer({
  url: "https://mi-servidor.com/datos.kml",
  map: map,
  preserveViewport: false,
  suppressInfoWindows: false
});

// Heatmap (requiere librería visualization)
const { HeatmapLayer } = await google.maps.importLibrary("visualization");
const heatmap = new HeatmapLayer({
  data: [
    new google.maps.LatLng(-33.45, -70.65),
    new google.maps.LatLng(-33.44, -70.64),
    // ... más puntos
  ],
  map: map,
  radius: 20,
  opacity: 0.8
});

// Data Layer (GeoJSON)
map.data.loadGeoJson("https://mi-servidor.com/datos.geojson");
map.data.setStyle((feature) => ({
  fillColor: feature.getProperty("color") || "blue",
  strokeColor: "black",
  strokeWeight: 1,
  fillOpacity: 0.5
}));
map.data.addListener("click", (event) => {
  console.log("Feature:", event.feature.getProperty("name"));
});
```

### 2.5 Servicios Integrados

#### Geocoder (dentro de JS API):
```javascript
const geocoder = new google.maps.Geocoder();

// Geocodificar dirección
const response = await geocoder.geocode({
  address: "Av. Kennedy 7100, Vitacura, Chile"
});
const location = response.results[0].geometry.location;
console.log(location.lat(), location.lng());

// Reverse geocoding
const response2 = await geocoder.geocode({
  location: { lat: -33.4078, lng: -70.5755 }
});
console.log(response2.results[0].formatted_address);
```

#### Directions Service:
```javascript
const directionsService = new google.maps.DirectionsService();
const directionsRenderer = new google.maps.DirectionsRenderer({ map: map });

const result = await directionsService.route({
  origin: "Santiago, Chile",
  destination: "Valparaíso, Chile",
  waypoints: [{ location: "Viña del Mar, Chile", stopover: true }],
  travelMode: google.maps.TravelMode.DRIVING,  // DRIVING, WALKING, BICYCLING, TRANSIT
  avoidTolls: false,
  avoidHighways: false,
  provideRouteAlternatives: true
});
directionsRenderer.setDirections(result);

// Extraer datos
const route = result.routes[0];
const leg = route.legs[0];
console.log("Distancia:", leg.distance.text);
console.log("Duración:", leg.duration.text);
console.log("Inicio:", leg.start_address);
console.log("Fin:", leg.end_address);
```

#### Distance Matrix Service:
```javascript
const service = new google.maps.DistanceMatrixService();
const response = await service.getDistanceMatrix({
  origins: ["Santiago, Chile", "Valparaíso, Chile"],
  destinations: ["Viña del Mar, Chile", "Concón, Chile"],
  travelMode: google.maps.TravelMode.DRIVING,
  unitSystem: google.maps.UnitSystem.METRIC
});

response.rows.forEach((row, i) => {
  row.elements.forEach((element, j) => {
    console.log(`${response.originAddresses[i]} → ${response.destinationAddresses[j]}`);
    console.log(`  Distancia: ${element.distance.text}, Tiempo: ${element.duration.text}`);
  });
});
```

#### Elevation Service:
```javascript
const elevator = new google.maps.ElevationService();
const response = await elevator.getElevationForLocations({
  locations: [{ lat: -33.4078, lng: -70.5755 }]
});
console.log("Elevación:", response.results[0].elevation, "metros");

// Elevation along path
const pathResponse = await elevator.getElevationAlongPath({
  path: [{ lat: -33.45, lng: -70.65 }, { lat: -33.40, lng: -70.55 }],
  samples: 100
});
```

### 2.6 Librerías

```javascript
// Importar librerías bajo demanda
const { Map } = await google.maps.importLibrary("maps");
const { AdvancedMarkerElement } = await google.maps.importLibrary("marker");
const { StreetViewPanorama } = await google.maps.importLibrary("streetView");
const { HeatmapLayer } = await google.maps.importLibrary("visualization");
const { DrawingManager } = await google.maps.importLibrary("drawing");
const { spherical, encoding, poly } = await google.maps.importLibrary("geometry");
const { Autocomplete, PlacesService } = await google.maps.importLibrary("places");
```

#### Geometry Library:
```javascript
// Distancia entre puntos (metros)
const distance = google.maps.geometry.spherical.computeDistanceBetween(
  new google.maps.LatLng(-33.45, -70.65),
  new google.maps.LatLng(-33.40, -70.55)
);
console.log("Distancia:", distance, "metros");

// Área de polígono (m²)
const area = google.maps.geometry.spherical.computeArea(polygon.getPath());

// Heading (rumbo) entre puntos
const heading = google.maps.geometry.spherical.computeHeading(from, to);

// Decodificar polyline
const path = google.maps.geometry.encoding.decodePath(encodedPolyline);
```

#### Drawing Library:
```javascript
const drawingManager = new google.maps.drawing.DrawingManager({
  drawingMode: google.maps.drawing.OverlayType.POLYGON,
  drawingControl: true,
  drawingControlOptions: {
    position: google.maps.ControlPosition.TOP_CENTER,
    drawingModes: ["marker", "circle", "polygon", "polyline", "rectangle"]
  }
});
drawingManager.setMap(map);

drawingManager.addListener("polygoncomplete", (polygon) => {
  const area = google.maps.geometry.spherical.computeArea(polygon.getPath());
  console.log("Área dibujada:", area, "m²");
});
```

