## 3. Geocoding API (REST)

### Base URL:
```
https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json
```

### Parámetros:
| Parámetro | Requerido | Descripción |
|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| `address` | Sí* | Dirección a geocodificar |
| `latlng` | Sí* | Coordenadas para reverse geocoding |
| `place_id` | Sí* | Place ID para obtener dirección |
| `components` | No | Filtro de componentes (country:CL) |
| `bounds` | No | Sesgar resultados por viewport |
| `language` | No | Idioma (es, en, pt, etc.) |
| `region` | No | Código de región (cl, ar, mx) |
| `key` | Sí | API key |

*Se requiere uno de: address, latlng, o place_id

### Ejemplos:
```bash
# Geocodificar dirección
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json?address=Av+Kennedy+7100,Vitacura,Chile&key=API_KEY

# Reverse geocoding
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json?latlng=-33.4078,-70.5755&language=es&key=API_KEY

# Con filtro de componentes
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json?address=Mapocho+5817&components=country:CL&key=API_KEY
```

### Respuesta:
```json
{
  "results": [{
    "formatted_address": "Av. Presidente Kennedy 7100, Vitacura, Región Metropolitana, Chile",
    "geometry": {
      "location": { "lat": -33.4078, "lng": -70.5755 },
      "location_type": "ROOFTOP",
      "viewport": { "northeast": {...}, "southwest": {...} }
    },
    "place_id": "ChIJ...",
    "address_components": [
      { "long_name": "7100", "short_name": "7100", "types": ["street_number"] },
      { "long_name": "Avenida Presidente Kennedy", "types": ["route"] },
      { "long_name": "Vitacura", "types": ["locality"] }
    ],
    "types": ["street_address"]
  }],
  "status": "OK"
}
```

