## 4. Places API (New)

### Text Search:
```bash
POST https://places.googleapis.com/v1/places:searchText
Headers:
  X-Goog-Api-Key: API_KEY
  X-Goog-FieldMask: places.displayName,places.formattedAddress,places.location,places.rating
Body:
{
  "textQuery": "restaurantes en Las Condes Santiago Chile",
  "languageCode": "es",
  "maxResultCount": 10,
  "locationBias": {
    "circle": {
      "center": { "latitude": -33.41, "longitude": -70.57 },
      "radius": 5000
    }
  }
}
```

### Nearby Search:
```bash
POST https://places.googleapis.com/v1/places:searchNearby
Headers:
  X-Goog-Api-Key: API_KEY
  X-Goog-FieldMask: places.displayName,places.types,places.location
Body:
{
  "includedTypes": ["restaurant", "cafe"],
  "maxResultCount": 20,
  "locationRestriction": {
    "circle": {
      "center": { "latitude": -33.4078, "longitude": -70.5755 },
      "radius": 1000
    }
  }
}
```

### Place Details:
```bash
GET https://places.googleapis.com/v1/places/ChIJ...?languageCode=es
Headers:
  X-Goog-Api-Key: API_KEY
  X-Goog-FieldMask: displayName,formattedAddress,rating,userRatingCount,
                     regularOpeningHours,photos,websiteUri,nationalPhoneNumber,
                     priceLevel,editorialSummary
```

### Autocomplete:
```bash
POST https://places.googleapis.com/v1/places:autocomplete
Headers:
  X-Goog-Api-Key: API_KEY
Body:
{
  "input": "Av Kennedy",
  "languageCode": "es",
  "includedRegionCodes": ["cl"],
  "locationBias": {
    "circle": {
      "center": { "latitude": -33.45, "longitude": -70.65 },
      "radius": 50000
    }
  }
}
```

### Tipos de Places populares:
restaurant, cafe, bar, hotel, hospital, pharmacy, school, university,
bank, atm, gas_station, parking, supermarket, shopping_mall, gym,
park, museum, church, police, fire_station, airport, train_station,
bus_station, subway_station, library, post_office, dentist, doctor

