## 5. Routes API (Reemplazo de Directions + Distance Matrix)

### Compute Routes:
```bash
POST https://routes.googleapis.com/directions/v2:computeRoutes
Headers:
  X-Goog-Api-Key: API_KEY
  X-Goog-FieldMask: routes.duration,routes.distanceMeters,routes.polyline,
                     routes.legs.steps,routes.travelAdvisory
Body:
{
  "origin": {
    "location": { "latLng": { "latitude": -33.45, "longitude": -70.65 } }
  },
  "destination": {
    "location": { "latLng": { "latitude": -33.0472, "longitude": -71.6127 } }
  },
  "travelMode": "DRIVE",
  "routingPreference": "TRAFFIC_AWARE",
  "computeAlternativeRoutes": true,
  "languageCode": "es",
  "units": "METRIC"
}
```

### Travel Modes:
| Modo | Descripción |
|------|-------------|
| `DRIVE` | Automóvil |
| `BICYCLE` | Bicicleta |
| `WALK` | A pie |
| `TRANSIT` | Transporte público |
| `TWO_WHEELER` | Moto/scooter |

### Compute Route Matrix:
```bash
POST https://routes.googleapis.com/distanceMatrix/v2:computeRouteMatrix
Headers:
  X-Goog-Api-Key: API_KEY
  X-Goog-FieldMask: originIndex,destinationIndex,duration,distanceMeters,status
Body:
{
  "origins": [
    { "waypoint": { "location": { "latLng": { "latitude": -33.45, "longitude": -70.65 } } } },
    { "waypoint": { "location": { "latLng": { "latitude": -33.41, "longitude": -70.57 } } } }
  ],
  "destinations": [
    { "waypoint": { "location": { "latLng": { "latitude": -33.05, "longitude": -71.61 } } } }
  ],
  "travelMode": "DRIVE"
}
```

