## 6. Elevation API

```bash
# Elevación de puntos
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/elevation/json?locations=-33.4078,-70.5755|-33.45,-70.65&key=API_KEY

# Elevación a lo largo de un path
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/elevation/json?path=-33.45,-70.65|-33.40,-70.55&samples=50&key=API_KEY

# Respuesta:
{
  "results": [{
    "elevation": 632.45,
    "location": { "lat": -33.4078, "lng": -70.5755 },
    "resolution": 4.77
  }],
  "status": "OK"
}
```

