## 7. Maps Static API

```bash
# Mapa estático básico
https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=-33.4078,-70.5755&zoom=16&size=640x480&maptype=roadmap&key=API_KEY

# Con marcadores
https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=-33.45,-70.65&zoom=12&size=640x480&markers=color:red|label:A|-33.4078,-70.5755&markers=color:blue|label:B|-33.41,-70.53&key=API_KEY

# Con path (línea)
https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?size=640x480&path=color:0xff0000ff|weight:3|-33.45,-70.65|-33.40,-70.55|-33.41,-70.57&key=API_KEY

# Satellite
https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=-33.4078,-70.5755&zoom=18&size=640x480&maptype=satellite&key=API_KEY

# Con estilo custom
https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=-33.45,-70.65&zoom=13&size=640x480&style=feature:road|color:0x000000&style=feature:water|color:0x0000ff&key=API_KEY
```

### Parámetros:
| Parámetro | Descripción |
|-----------|-------------|
| `center` | Centro del mapa (lat,lng o dirección) |
| `zoom` | 0-21 |
| `size` | WxH píxeles (máx 640x640, o 2048x2048 con scale=2) |
| `scale` | 1 o 2 (retina) |
| `format` | png, png8, png32, gif, jpg, jpg-baseline |
| `maptype` | roadmap, satellite, terrain, hybrid |
| `markers` | Marcadores (color, label, size, location) |
| `path` | Líneas/polígonos |
| `style` | Estilos del mapa |
| `visible` | Ubicaciones que deben ser visibles |

