## 8. Map Tiles API

### Tipos de Tiles:
| Tipo | Descripción |
|------|-------------|
| **2D Tiles** | Roadmap y satellite tiles |
| **Photorealistic 3D Tiles** | Tiles 3D fotorrealistas (OGC 3D Tiles/glTF) |
| **Street View Tiles** | Tiles de Street View panorámicos |

### Photorealistic 3D Tiles con CesiumJS:
```javascript
// Root tileset URL
const TILES_URL = `https://tile.googleapis.com/v1/3dtiles/root.json?key=${API_KEY}`;

const viewer = new Cesium.Viewer("cesiumContainer", {
  globe: false  // Desactivar globo default
});

const tileset = await Cesium.Cesium3DTileset.fromUrl(TILES_URL);
viewer.scene.primitives.add(tileset);

// Volar a ubicación
viewer.camera.flyTo({
  destination: Cesium.Cartesian3.fromDegrees(-70.5755, -33.4078, 1000),
  orientation: { heading: Cesium.Math.toRadians(0), pitch: Cesium.Math.toRadians(-45) }
});
```

