## 10. Pricing (USD por 1,000 requests)

| API | Costo | Free tier |
|-----|-------|-----------|
| Maps JavaScript (Dynamic) | $7.00 | ~28,500/mes |
| Maps Static | $2.00 | ~100,000/mes |
| Street View Static | $7.00 | ~28,500/mes |
| Geocoding | $5.00 | ~40,000/mes |
| Places Text Search | $32.00 | ~6,250/mes |
| Places Nearby Search | $32.00 | ~6,250/mes |
| Places Details (Basic) | $17.00 | ~11,750/mes |
| Places Autocomplete | $2.83 | ~70,600/mes |
| Routes Compute | $5.00-$10.00 | ~20,000/mes |
| Route Matrix | $5.00-$10.00 | ~20,000/mes |
| Elevation | $5.00 | ~40,000/mes |
| Directions | $5.00-$10.00 | ~20,000/mes |
| Distance Matrix | $5.00-$10.00 | ~20,000/mes |

**Free tier**: $200 USD/mes de crédito gratuito de Google Maps Platform.

